title: Bank of AJK signs MoU with Malaysian firm - Business - DAWN.COM
content:
MUZAFFARABAD: The state-owned Bank of Azad Jammu and Kashmir (BoAJK) has taken a significant step towards acquiring a scheduling licence and embracing digitalisation by signing a MemoraÂ­ndum of Understanding (MoU) with Silverlake Axis, a globally renowned Malaysian company.

The MoU was signed during a ceremony held in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia, followed by an exchange of documents, according to a press release issued by BoAJK spokesperson Ghulamullah Kiyani on Thursday.

Published in Dawn, May 30th, 2025
